casebody.data:
In re ALLEN. GROSS, Appellant, v. TOTMAN, Respondent. (Supreme Court General Term, Fourth Department. May 18, 1894.) Final accounting of Van Burén Gross, as sole surviving assignee of William H. Allen.

Argued before HARDIN, P. J., and MARTIN and MERWIN, JJ.

No opinion. Order affirmed, with $10 costs and disbursements.
